localString.value:
This region is for the new custom encounter system that works with the DMFI Encounter wand and widget. It allows you to set up 9 encounters in this region and then they can be called using the DMFI Encounter wand. You can adjust them at any time during the game to find a good balance. The ditto widget will work with these encounters as well.
To set them up, place monsters in (or immediately around) each stone circle. That is it. ALL will spawn. There is NO scaling to the system. You can go into the toolset and change the name of the WAYPOINT to match the name of your encounter.
DO NOT MIX FACTIONS HERE. That is the reason for the raised terrain. Hostiles on one side and Commoners on the other. You can mix factions IF you shut off the creature AI, but this takes good timing and planning.
You look about you, suspicious, but see nothing.
Do not pass Go. Do not collect 200 dollars.
